title: GUMMY Jelly LED/UV Diamonds Gel, Base Coat, Shine E Top Coat, Matte Top Coat
description: *CURRENT FORMULA/BOTTLES FROM ENAIL COUTURE* See photos for details. GUMMY JELLY is a gel that you apply to your nails to secure diamonds, rhinestones and charms. Gummy Jelly is practical application for any size of embellishments and they don't even move! Cure for 60-90 seconds in any LED/UV lamp. Apply ShineE Gel to seal it all in. SHINEE GEL is the BEST no wipe, soak off top gel in the WORLD and #1 FOR CHROME! Save time in application by using the ShineE Gel No-Cleanse Sealer with either Gel or Acrylic. Added UV Brighteners sure to enhance the vivid whites, lucent clears, and radiant pinks. This gel top coat seals and protects your gel designs and gives a beautiful glossy look. It prevents coloration and discoloration from everyday use. Apply thin coat of ShineE top gel and cure for 1 minute under UV lamp or cure 30 seconds under LED lamp. BASE GEL creates the adhesive bond between the nail plate and gel products without damaging the nail plate. You do not need to remove any sticky residue or worry about the product shrinkage. Apply thin coat of Base Gel and cure for 1 minute under UV lamp or cure 30 seconds under LED lamp. VELVET MATTE TOP GEL will transform any gel color and design to a sleek shine free, velvet like matte finish. It seals and protects your gel design and prevents coloration and discoloration from everyday use. No need to remove residue with velvet after curing. Velvet is a wipe free gel top coat and can work with any gel polish! UV/LED cure 1-2 minutes.
